\c 34
\s Kufa nekuvigwa kwaMozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mozisi wakakwira kubva pamapani ekwaMoabhu achienda kugomo reNebho, panhongonya yePisiga pakatarisana neJeriko. Jehovha ndokumutaridza nyika yese yeGiriyadhi, kusvika kuDhani,
\v 2 neNafutari yese, nenyika yaEfuremu, naManase, nenyika yese yaJudha kusvika pagungwa rekupedzisira;
\v 3 nechamhembe, neBani remupata weJeriko, guta remichindwe kusvika Zoari.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha akati kwaari: Iyi inyika yandakapikira Abhurahama, Isaka, naJakove ndichiti: Ndichaipa kumbeu yako; ndakakuita kuti uone nemeso ako, asi haungayambukiriko.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Mozisi muranda waJehovha wakafirapo munyika yaMoabhu zvichienderana neshoko naJehovha.
\v 6 Zvino wakamuviga pamupata panyika yaMoabhu, pakatarisana neBheti-Peori, asi hakuna munhu anoziva rinda rake kusvika nhasi.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Mozisi waiva wemakore zana nemakumi maviri pakufa kwake; meso ake akange asati osvibirirwa, nesimba rake risati roderera.
\p
\v 8 Vana vaIsraeri vakachema Mozisi pamapani ekwaMoabhu mazuva makumi matatu; saizvozvo mazuva emariro ekuchema Mozisi akapera.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Joshua mwanakomana waNuni wakange azere nemweya wekuchenjera; nokuti Mozisi wakange aisa maoko ake pamusoro pake; vana vaIsraeri ndokumuteerera, ndokuita Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi.
\p
\v 10 Zvino hakuna kumuka muporofita kubva pakati paIsraeri wakaita saMozisi, Jehovha waakaziva chiso nechiso;
\v 11 pazviratidzo zvese nezvishamiso, Jehovha zvaakamutuma kunoita panyika yeEgipita, kuna Farao nekuvaranda vake vese nekunyika yake yese;
\v 12 neparuoko rwese urwo rwune simba, nepakutyisa kukuru kwese Mozisi kwaakaita pamberi pemeso aIsraeri wese.
